title: S15 Ep110: Supernatural News/Parashare: Batman, Monkey Man, and the World's Largest Bigfoot Edition
itunes:title: Supernatural News/Parashare: Batman, Monkey Man, and the World's Largest Bigfoot Edition
description:
Ho, Ho, Hold the Presses! Darkness Radio Supernatural News & ParaShare is here with Batman, Monkey Man and The World's Largest Bigfoot Edition!
Dave & Tim are in a festive mood as they break down this weeks unusual news from around the world. 

Scientists have narrowed it down, they have either located an intelligent planet...or, they haven't. Seems science is as noncommittal as Tim's proposal to any of the women Dave offers to him from his vast list of single Stupid Criminals list. 

What do Batman and a famous piece of UFO footage have in common? Is there a Cryptid Crisis in Singapore?

For answers to this and more things you didn't know you needed to know tune in for fun and YOUR paranormal encounters Holiday Style!
